.DT
set_leader
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_leader

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_leader -  This function allows you to set a new leader for the group.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs int set_leader(string name,
object person,
object appointer)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the group
%^BOLD%^person%^RESET%^ - the new leader
%^BOLD%^appointer%^RESET%^ - if this != 0, group is told he set the new leader

.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 if the group doesn't exist

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/group_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function allows you to set a new leader for the group.

.EP

